---
// src/components/about/AboutStory.astro
---
<section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-white dark:bg-black transition-colors duration-300 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="px-6 md:px-12 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-20 items-center">
        
        <div class="order-2 lg:order-1">
            <div class="flex items-center space-x-4 mb-6">
                <div class="w-12 h-1 bg-[#f0ba18]"></div>
                <span class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-widest text-sm font-bold">Nuestra Trayectoria</span>
            </div>
            
            <h2 class="font-brand text-2xl md:text-4xl text-gray-900 dark:text-white uppercase mb-6 leading-tight">
                4 Años de <span class="text-[#f0ba18]">Evolución Constante</span>
            </h2>
            
            <div class="space-y-6 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-lg leading-relaxed text-justify font-sans">
                <p>
                    La historia de <strong>Grupo Transporte RG</strong> comenzó el <strong>10 de julio de 2021</strong>. Mientras el mundo cambiaba, nosotros vimos la oportunidad de crear un servicio logístico diferente: más humano, más seguro y verdaderamente comprometido.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Empezamos con una visión clara y mucha determinación. Hoy, nos hemos consolidado como un referente en el sector, aprendiendo que la tecnología es vital, pero que la confianza se construye kilómetro a kilómetro.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 mt-8">
                
                <div class="bg-white dark:bg-zinc-900 p-5 rounded-2xl shadow-md border border-border border-l-4 border-l-[#f0ba18] hover:-translate-y-1 transition-transform duration-300">
                    <span class="block text-3xl md:text-4xl font-brand text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-1">+4</span>
                    <span class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 font-medium">Años de Experiencia</span>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-white dark:bg-zinc-900 p-5 rounded-2xl shadow-md border border-border border-l-4 border-l-[#f0ba18] hover:-translate-y-1 transition-transform duration-300">
                    <span class="block text-3xl md:text-4xl font-brand text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-1">100%</span>
                    <span class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 font-medium">Cobertura Nacional</span>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="order-1 lg:order-2 relative group">
    
    <div class="absolute -top-6 -right-6 w-full h-full border-2 border-brand/30 rounded-[2.5rem] -z-10 hidden md:block group-hover:top-0 group-hover:right-0 transition-all duration-700"></div>

    <div class="relative h-[450px] lg:h-[600px] w-full rounded-[2.5rem] overflow-hidden shadow-[0_20px_50px_rgba(0,0,0,0.3)] dark:shadow-[0_20px_50px_rgba(0,0,0,0.8)] border-4 border-white dark:border-zinc-900 transform lg:rotate-3 group-hover:rotate-0 transition-all duration-700 ease-out">
        
        <img 
            src="/img/historia-rg.jpg" 
            alt="Historia Grupo Transporte RG" 
            class="w-full h-full object-cover object-center 
                   sepia-[0.25] saturate-[0.9] contrast-[1.1]
                   group-hover:sepia-0 group-hover:saturate-100 group-hover:scale-110 
                   transition-all duration-1000 ease-in-out"
        />

        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/90 via-black/20 to-transparent opacity-80 group-hover:opacity-40 transition-opacity duration-700"></div>

        <div class="absolute bottom-8 left-8 right-8 transform translate-y-6 group-hover:translate-y-0 transition-transform duration-700">
            <p class="text-brand font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-xs mb-2">Compromiso RG</p>
            <h3 class="text-white text-2xl font-bold leading-tight drop-shadow-md">
                Conectando cada rincón <br/> de nuestra tierra.
            </h3>
        </div>

        <div class="absolute top-6 left-6 backdrop-blur-md bg-white/10 border border-white/20 px-5 py-3 rounded-2xl shadow-xl">
            <span class="block text-brand text-2xl font-bold leading-none">2021</span>
            <span class="block text-white text-[10px] uppercase tracking-tighter mt-1 font-medium">Est. 10 de Julio</span>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="absolute -bottom-10 -right-10 w-32 h-32 bg-brand/10 rounded-full blur-3xl -z-10 group-hover:bg-brand/20 transition-colors duration-700"></div>
</div>
    </div>
</section>